Welcome and well met!

38 year old Houstonian here. I primarily play on The Rathe. I've just
started on my epic. I'm glad I can jump around and do parts out of
order. I guess that's a benefit of being a druid ;)

If you're ever on the Rathe, look me up.

Timmye Cousteau - 45 halfling druid
Keiyuki Harlok - 29 wood elf warrior
Stabbitystab Endebache - 27 dark elf rogue
Hepkat Daddio - 20 Vah Shir Bard
